od to bear phi-features, as well as how tense limits PRO’s distribution in a here-to-fore unnoticed fashion.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aControl (Linguistics) 0aControl (Linguistics). 0aGrammar, Comparative and generalxInfinitival constructions. 0aGrammar, Comparative and general. 0aPragmatics. 4aControl Theory. 4aGenerative Grammatik. 4aSyntax. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aControl Theory.  aGenerative Grammar.  aSemantics.  aSyntax.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013z978311031724408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK 2013z9783110317237oZDB-23-DSP0 cprintz978161451042040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161451041340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781614510413423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781614510413/original  a978-3-11-023845-7  DGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031724-4  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013b2013  a978-3-11-074296-1  De Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015c2000d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DG